IDEAL BIKE CORP (8933)  said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 56.83% to NT$132,466,000 from NT$306,842,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            132,466          306,842    
YOY%             -56.83%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            727,610         1,073,812   
YOY%             -32.24% 
=================================================================
 